This example code performs a two-dimensional lattice Boltzmann simulation of flow in a lid-driven square cavity.

See:
J. Milthorpe and A.P. Rendell (2012). Efficient update of ghost regions using active messages (preprint), in proceedings of the 19th IEEE International Conference on High Performance Computing (HiPC). 

Dependencies
------------
This example requires the addition of ghost region support to the X10 array library, as described in Milthorpe and Rendell (2012).  See ghostRegions.patch

